<emphasis id="33A7CD77FFE5393DEE32C0B9FAC15C92" bold="true" box="[1283,1342,1930,1956]" pageId="75" pageNumber="76">C–H</emphasis>
. “Stone City beds”, Stone City Bluff, Brazos River, Texas, paratypes (IRSNB P 10159–10164). 
